targets.queryText:
SELECT 
    -- Temperature Data for SensorA
    CASE 
        WHEN CAST(t.SensorAir AS FLOAT) = -1 THEN NULL 
        ELSE CAST(t.SensorAir AS FLOAT) 
    END AS Temp,
    -- Humidity Data for SensorA
    CASE 
        WHEN CAST(h.SensorAir AS INTEGER) = -1 THEN NULL 
        ELSE CAST(h.SensorAir AS INTEGER) 
    END AS Hum
FROM 
    (SELECT * FROM TemperatureData ORDER BY id DESC LIMIT 1) t
CROSS JOIN 
    (SELECT * FROM HumidityData ORDER BY id DESC LIMIT 1) h;

SELECT 
    -- Temperature Data
    CASE WHEN CAST(t.SensorA_1 AS FLOAT) = -1 THEN NULL ELSE CAST(t.SensorA_1 AS FLOAT) END AS "Temp 1",
    CASE WHEN CAST(h.SensorA_1 AS INTEGER) = -1 THEN NULL ELSE CAST(h.SensorA_1 AS INTEGER) END AS "Hum 1",
    CASE WHEN CAST(t.SensorA_2 AS FLOAT) = -1 THEN NULL ELSE CAST(t.SensorA_2 AS FLOAT) END AS "Temp 2",
    CASE WHEN CAST(h.SensorA_2 AS INTEGER) = -1 THEN NULL ELSE CAST(h.SensorA_2 AS INTEGER) END AS "Hum 2",
    CASE WHEN CAST(t.SensorA_3 AS FLOAT) = -1 THEN NULL ELSE CAST(t.SensorA_3 AS FLOAT) END AS "Temp 3",
    CASE WHEN CAST(h.SensorA_3 AS INTEGER) = -1 THEN NULL ELSE CAST(h.SensorA_3 AS INTEGER) END AS "Hum 3",
    CASE WHEN CAST(t.SensorA_4 AS FLOAT) = -1 THEN NULL ELSE CAST(t.SensorA_4 AS FLOAT) END AS "Temp 4",
    CASE WHEN CAST(h.SensorA_4 AS INTEGER) = -1 THEN NULL ELSE CAST(h.SensorA_4 AS INTEGER) END AS "Hum 4"
FROM 
    (SELECT * FROM TemperatureData ORDER BY id DESC LIMIT 1) t
CROSS JOIN 
    (SELECT * FROM HumidityData ORDER BY id DESC LIMIT 1) h;

targets.queryText:
SELECT 
    -- Temperature Data
    CASE WHEN CAST(t.SensorC_1 AS FLOAT) = -1 THEN NULL ELSE CAST(t.SensorC_1 AS FLOAT) END AS "Temp 1",
    CASE WHEN CAST(h.SensorC_1 AS INTEGER) = -1 THEN NULL ELSE CAST(h.SensorC_1 AS INTEGER) END AS "Hum 1",
    CASE WHEN CAST(t.SensorC_2 AS FLOAT) = -1 THEN NULL ELSE CAST(t.SensorC_2 AS FLOAT) END AS "Temp 2",
    CASE WHEN CAST(h.SensorC_2 AS INTEGER) = -1 THEN NULL ELSE CAST(h.SensorC_2 AS INTEGER) END AS "Hum 2",
    CASE WHEN CAST(t.SensorC_3 AS FLOAT) = -1 THEN NULL ELSE CAST(t.SensorC_3 AS FLOAT) END AS "Temp 3",
    CASE WHEN CAST(h.SensorC_3 AS INTEGER) = -1 THEN NULL ELSE CAST(h.SensorC_3 AS INTEGER) END AS "Hum 3",
    CASE WHEN CAST(t.SensorC_4 AS FLOAT) = -1 THEN NULL ELSE CAST(t.SensorC_4 AS FLOAT) END AS "Temp 4",
    CASE WHEN CAST(h.SensorC_4 AS INTEGER) = -1 THEN NULL ELSE CAST(h.SensorC_4 AS INTEGER) END AS "Hum 4"
FROM 
    (SELECT * FROM TemperatureData ORDER BY id DESC LIMIT 1) t
CROSS JOIN 
    (SELECT * FROM HumidityData ORDER BY id DESC LIMIT 1) h;
